{"tid":1348141,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朗屏站外面泊左一堆狗車","createTime":"2019-07-22T07:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T09:24:28.000Z","uid":238370,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0478ea6a9676f2ff01c4c9176634b2c17821998b","tid":1348141,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4BbUn0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4BbUn0f.png&h=7d938d55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一陣古惑仔打人，就拉我地番狗竇"},{"pid":"c469a373ab5736c036724f92de9bd26151f83c02","tid":1348141,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:42:00.000Z","msg":"網上流傳元朗朗屏附近下午會有事情發生，約30名警員進入朗屏西鐵站戒備，表示要在此維持秩序。他們身穿黃色反光背心、戴帽，沒有頭盔或盾牌。<br />\n<br />\n有市民上前批評警員昨晚不到元朗站執法，致電報警又無人接聽，執法不力，令市民遇襲受傷，朗屏站內多間商店已落閘暫停營業。<br />\n<br />\n另外，社工界發起在朗屏站集合，稍後集體到元朗警署報案。"},{"pid":"da8b21f7c7239f074c3bd6c028f56a04a4eab133","tid":1348141,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"重要 推"},{"pid":"affcc5b0ab082a2fddea70595a04662e7ad912ab","tid":1348141,"uid":238370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da8b21f7c7239f074c3bd6c028f56a04a4eab133","tid":1348141,"uid":217418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"重要 推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:24:28.000Z","msg":"走哂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}